# ─── Portfolio setup ($0 hosting) ────────────────────────────────────────────
#   Netlify Free     → frontend (already deployed)
#   Neon Free        → Postgres (DATABASE_URL in backend/.env)
#   Your PC          → backend + Whisper (RTX 3060)
#   Cloudflare Tunnel → free HTTPS to localhost:4000
#
# Quick start on your PC (two terminals):
#   npm run portfolio          ← prints checklist
#   npm run start:backend      ← terminal 1
#   npm run tunnel             ← terminal 2, copy https URL to Netlify BACKEND_URL
#
# Local full stack (no tunnel):
#   npm run dev:backend        → http://localhost:4000
#   npm run dev:frontend       → http://localhost:3000
#
# Database: run database/migrations/000 then 001 in Neon SQL Editor
